NK001(ka)026:0: so thar sdom brgyud kyi gsol 'debs bzhugs /
NK001(ka)026:1: mtshan dpe'i gzugs sku mthong dang tshangs dbyangs gsung //
NK001(ka)026:2: lhan cig thos pa'i mod la srid zhi'i gdung //
NK001(ka)026:3: rab bsal khyod thugs rnam mkhyen la sbyor ba //
NK001(ka)026:4: kun mkhyen nyi ma'i gnyen la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:5: sh+aa ri'i bu dang rgyal rigs sgra gcan 'dzin //
NK001(ka)026:6: bram ze'i btsun pa r+aa hu la gup+ta //
NK001(ka)026:7: 'phags mchog klu sgrub slob dpon legs ldan 'bye. //
NK001(ka)026:8: dpal sbas ye shes snying por gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:9: gangs can bstan pa'i nyi ma zhi ba 'tsho //
NK001(ka)026:10: rba rigs rat+na gtsang pa rab gsal zhabs //
NK001(ka)026:11: sh+aakya mu ne g.yor po dge ba 'byung //
NK001(ka)026:12: dgongs pa rab gsal zhabs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:13: klu mes tshul she rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang //
NK001(ka)026:14: sne 0 grags rgyal 'bre chen shes rab 'bar //
NK001(ka)026:15: brtson 'grus 'bar dang gzhon nu seng ge'i zhabs //
NK001(ka)026:16: gro ston bdud rtsi grags la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:17: mchims chen nam mkha' grags dang grags sher ba //
NK001(ka)026:18: mchims ston blo bzang grags pa kun rgyal rje //
NK001(ka)026:19: grub pa shes rab pan chen dge 'dun grub //
NK001(ka)026:20: gnas snying kun dag'i mtshan la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:21: dge 'dun rgya mtsho dge legs dpal bzang po //
NK001(ka)026:22: dpal 'byor rgya mtsho dkon mchog chos 'phel dang //
NK001(ka)026:23: dkon mchog bstan 'dzin ngag dbang chos kyi dpal //
NK001(ka)026:24: chos kyi grags pa rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:25: 'gyur med chos ldan o rgyan bstan 'dzin rje //
NK001(ka)026:26: rig 'dzin bzang po pad+ma mad+ga la //
NK001(ka)026:27: thub bstan nyin byed gzhan phan mtha' yas sde //
NK001(ka)026:28: thub bstan rgyal mtshan zhabs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:29: mtshungs med kun dga' tshul khrims rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK001(ka)026:30: rdo rje 'dzin pa ngag dbang nor bu'i dpal //
NK001(ka)026:31: bka' drin mnyam med phan bde'i 'od zer te //
NK001(ka)026:32: mkhan brgyud dam pa rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK001(ka)026:33: ngan song gnas gsum sdug basngala drag pos mnar //
NK001(ka)026:34: mi dang 'dod lha 'gyur ba'i duhkhasa gzir //
NK001(ka)026:35: gzugs dang gzugs med 'du byed 'chings bas bcings //
NK001(ka)026:36: 'khor ba'i rang mtshan mngon sum mthong bar shog /
NK001(ka)026:37: tshul des bcos min yid 'byung nges pa lnga //
NK001(ka)026:38: yongs bral da chog sgo nas gsol bzhi'i las //
NK001(ka)026:39: 'khrul med cho gas tshangs spyod dpal thob ste //
NK001(ka)026:40: ngur smrig 'dzin pa'i mchog tu 'gyur bar shog /
NK001(ka)026:41: mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i bsod snyoms zas kyis 'tsho //
NK001(ka)026:42: shing drung cog pu tsam gyi gnas mal dang //
NK001(ka)026:43: rnyed sla phyag bdar khrod pa'i dur smrig gos //
NK001(ka)026:44: gzhan gyis spyad zin sman la bsten par shog /
NK001(ka)026:45: pham pa bzhi dang lhag ma bcu gsum grangs //
NK001(ka)026:46: spang ltung sum cu ltung byed bcu phrag dgu /
NK001(ka)026:47: sor bshags bzhi dang nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis //
NK001(ka)026:48: bag yod brtan pos tshul bzhin bsrung bar shog /
NK001(ka)026:49: gzhan gyis khro dang mtshon sogs nye bar brdeg /
NK001(ka)026:50: gshegs dang mtshang 'dru la sogs gnod kun la //
NK001(ka)026:51: dran shes brtan pos gnyen po legs bsten nas //
NK001(ka)026:52: rtag tu bzod pa'i go cha bgo bar shog /
NK001(ka)026:53: mkhan slob dge ba'i bshes la mchog tu dad //
NK001(ka)026:54: tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod la gcig tu gus //
NK001(ka)026:55: sde snod lung la rab sbyangs bslab pa gsum //
NK001(ka)026:56: mngon par rtog pas bdag rgyud phyug par shog /
NK001(ka)026:57: bag yod mthun pa'i rlung gis tshul khrims gzings //
NK001(ka)026:58: mngon mtho'i rin chen gling bgrod thar ba'i nor //
NK001(ka)026:59: lhag bsam rgyal mtshan rtse mor yongs bkod nas //
NK001(ka)026:60: 'gro rnams phan bde'i 'dod rgus tshim byed shog /
NK001(ka)026:61: ces kun mkhyen lnga pa chen pos mdzad pa'i sdom rgyun gsol 'debs las /
NK001(ka)026:62: brgyud pa'i khyad par gyi zhi 'tsho yab sras kyi sh+lo ka gcig dang /
NK001(ka)026:63: dge 'dun rgya mtsho man gyi-sh+lo ka gcig bcas lo
NK001(ka)026:64: chen d+harma sh+r+ais bsgyur bar mdzad pa dang de nas
